{"tid":1381724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[10萬大軍]當遊行=非法集結,和理非已經準備加入抗爭","createTime":"2019-07-29T09:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:09:08.000Z","uid":244509,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bcca4aef1f29fe9222077a9a8469cd24cfce7463","tid":1381724,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:58:00.000Z","msg":"而家遊行例牌冇不反對通知書, 出得黎遊行既和理非都已經有心理準備被控非法集結, e個係一個契機, 壯大抗爭隊伍<br />\n<br />\n而家需要既係逐步誘導, 首要降低參與成本, 令更多人可以留低, 目前前線已經進化太多, 令素人卻步<br />\n<br />\n和理非第一個心理關口係守防線, 如果黎緊星期日前線可以改變策略, 透過文宣向和理非表明當警方出黑旗射催淚彈時, 大家會一齊後退, 唔守防線<br />\n想像下由港島西一路退向港島東, 一路後退線既話大概都要3,4個鐘, 咁對重裝防暴黎講係好大既體力消耗<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔夠皮ge話仲可以搭地鐵過海去將軍澳或尖沙咀繼續遊行, 反正同樣是非法集結, wfc? 咁樣班狗又要重新佈防<br />\n<br />\n如果前線覺得可以既話, 大家可以做下文宣, 出下圖, 加d標語, 例如:<br />\n'保護年青人', '珍惜前線', '齊上齊落', '與你同行'<br />\n<br />\n希望咁樣可以壯大抗爭隊伍, 將否決不反對通知書轉為契機, 冇效既話當俾前線休養番一星期, 之後重回勇武"},{"pid":"81c37317d2470efdd992ea885389993efc61f76c","tid":1381724,"uid":229019,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nxES6sr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnxES6sr.png&h=84b829c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSeS6sr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSeS6sr.jpg&h=cabdbd06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XYpc7s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XYpc7s.png&h=b81e00db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qud1fkN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqud1fkN.jpg&h=796d5146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hux9pd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHux9pd7.jpg&h=892a1f4f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6b69f45012bdd430fbd4ce47667dcaa88d94c1e","tid":1381724,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:05:10.000Z","msg":"（文宣幫手）Now元朗7分鐘 矛頭要指向 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警察&amp;鄉黑&amp;建制&amp;葉虎中聯辦</span></span> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380836\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380836</a><br />\n<br />\n - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c6f6657e2e517a83358efadc4a95e2551ee7bc4f","tid":1381724,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"},{"pid":"9e7aad0009c402afadb49062fb3f39795b9192da","tid":1381724,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:24:42.000Z","msg":"同埋唔駛遊行, 直接集結, 保留體力<br />\n狗一直既策略都係等和理非行完夠皮走哂先行動, 其他地方佢會hea你, 但而家個勢集結係中聯辦應該會即出"},{"pid":"bdc5e44e219a2d18b2fea396bf9e6435789db368","tid":1381724,"uid":244509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:58:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"278b5be6a1f17bd72a0dde8b40b1c4d68b2304dc","tid":1381724,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:02:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得最大問題似乎係冇明確的進攻目標"},{"pid":"233cdadd640217da61a4722ec04c57975a638a05","tid":1381724,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"278b5be6a1f17bd72a0dde8b40b1c4d68b2304dc","tid":1381724,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:02:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得最大問題似乎係冇明確的進攻目標"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:07:43.000Z","msg":"而家個勢集結係中聯辦d狗應該會即出"},{"pid":"68e814775d9f72f6557ff9911b0aae10e0217b12","tid":1381724,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:29:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6bc479a70c187bc1bc8effb5e0be40062e06af8","tid":1381724,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"233cdadd640217da61a4722ec04c57975a638a05","tid":1381724,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"278b5b